"title": "8253: faithfulness, examples of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8253",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those who show loyalty, reliability and devotion in their relationships with God and others.</p>\n<h2>Abraham</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:7-Neh9:8\">NEH 9:7–9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:9\">GAL 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:8-Heb11:12\">HEB 11:8–11:12</a></p>\n<h2>Moses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:5\">HEB 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:7\">NUM 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:24-Heb11:28\">HEB 11:24–11:28</a></p>\n<h2>Caleb</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:24\">NUM 14:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:36\">DEU 1:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:8-Josh14:9\">JOS 14:8–14:9</a></p>\n<h2>Elijah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a></p>\n<h2>David</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam29:6\">1SA 29:6</a></strong> <em>David, fleeing from Saul, shelters with Achish, king of Gath.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:6-2Sam9:7\">2SA 9:6–9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:22-2Sam22:24\">2SA 22:22–22:24</a></p>\n<h2>Hezekiah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:3\">2KI 20:3</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:3\">ISA 38:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:20\">2CH 31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:1\">2CH 32:1</a></p>\n<h2>Daniel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:4\">DAN 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:10\">DAN 6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Paul</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:12\">1TI 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:25\">1CO 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7\">2TI 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Timothy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:17\">1CO 4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:5\">2TI 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Silas</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">1PE 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25\">ACT 16:25</a></p>\n<h2>Christian martyrs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:13\">REV 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:11\">REV 12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Further examples</h2>\n<p>Enoch:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:22-Gen5:24\">GEN 5:22–5:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:5\">HEB 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">GEN 6:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:7\">HEB 11:7</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14-Josh24:15\">JOS 24:14–24:15</a> <em>Joshua</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:18\">1KI 19:18</a> <em>7,000 in Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:2\">2KI 22:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:2\">2CH 34:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:26\">2CH 35:26</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:13-Neh13:14\">NEH 13:13–13:14</a> <em>Nehemiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:11-Job23:12\">JOB 23:11–23:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:6\">JOB 27:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:2\">ISA 8:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:2\">2TI 2:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:16-Dan3:18\">DAN 3:16–3:18</a> <em>Shadrach, Meshach and Abednego</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:18-Acts4:20\">ACT 4:18–4:20</a> <em>Peter and John</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:21-Eph6:22\">EPH 6:21–6:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7\">COL 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:7\">COL 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:9\">COL 4:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:10-Phlm1:11\">PHM 1:10–1:11</a></p>",
